Package: findPC
Type: Package
Title: Determine the Optimal Number of PCs to Retain
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Haotian Zhuang, Zhicheng Ji
Maintainer: Haotian Zhuang <haotian.zhuang@duke.edu>
Description: findPC is a software tool including multiple metrics to automatically determine 
the optimal number of principal components to retain based on the standard deviations explained by each PC. 
A major advantage of findPC is that the only information required is a series of standard deviations explained by each PC.
License: 
Imports: ggplot2, cowplot
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
